Package com.complexible.common.hash

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractHasher
    An abstract Hasher implementation derived from the Guava AbstractHasher, which is packaged private, while this is public making it accessible for all implementors.
    AbstractPrimitiveSink
    Abstract implementation of a PrimitiveSink whose methods all throw UnsupportedOperationException.
    ConcatenatedPrimitiveSink<T extends PrimitiveSink>
    An implementation of PrimitiveSink which has a number of 'child' sinks to which each call to this Sink is delegated.
    HashCodeUtil
    Collected methods which allow easy implementation of hashCode.
